---
import { Scan, Smartphone, Wallet } from '@lucide/astro'
---

<section id="features" class="py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-surface-container-low mt-20 scroll-mt-20">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="mb-8 md:mb-16 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-on-surface">Designed for clarity.</h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg">Fintech doesn’t have to be loud to be effective.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 md:p-12 rounded-[3rem] flex flex-col justify-between group overflow-hidden relative hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform">
        <div class="space-y-6 max-w-md z-10">
          <Smartphone class="w-12 h-12 text-primary" />
          <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-on-surface">Daily awareness</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
            A gentle daily prompt keeps you aware of your spending. Add a note for context, then revisit your week or month at a glance. No budgets required.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
          <img
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            alt="Peaceful workspace"
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCHADUpU9_qcOETocUC23NxCdbAoLLTjBuYN6TsCSN85TSmfvTU4-SHScas3eg2Qbo3MvuukAKBbWyRX7kKXTYigu70woXe3QEB3hT7cjDZ-5wVbvNFzqziDlv26U8rohchRwHItIzQlAC-GUuV_Puq37nLt4znPaZVdQoxRye98YT4okQHju2ETgQqO0eMdXvhzCdDxl7botDPA5OzmwNwSdsMrWRzR5wZ1jXpcAq8cc7yh9e9Wt3jo-GM4quMpy0KafTZ4z5kch8"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-primary p-8 md:p-12 rounded-[3rem] flex flex-col justify-between text-on-primary hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform">
        <Wallet class="w-12 h-12" />
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold">Simple spend tracking</h3>
          <p class="text-on-primary/80 leading-relaxed">Log a purchase or set up a recurring entry for subscriptions. No spreadsheets, just clarity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 md:p-12 rounded-[3rem] flex flex-col justify-between shadow-sm border border-on-surface/5 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform">
        <Scan class="w-12 h-12 text-tertiary" />
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface">AI Receipt Scanning</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Snap a photo of any receipt and Spendful automatically extracts the amount. No manual entry needed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-secondary-container dark:bg-primary/10 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-[3rem] flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform">
        <div class="space-y-6 flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-on-surface tracking-tight">AI Spending Insights</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant">Get gentle reflections on your spending patterns. Designed to help you notice, not judge.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-64 h-48 rounded-4xl overflow-hidden shrink-0">
          <img
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            alt="Editorial insights"
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCYItl4pEyP2vB-5dKJyXcGzNnjv-r6NVitB-K1L3bbuFi8LJzhydQ7i5gOOXprTZrPNrq_ySKOBSVliKOwGToJ_tb7s-Nqhq-pgHlF7Upp3aywOiPgifQ2qhXadjpNEAox4lF77P1iyuACohNVbHi4GiBkIuTr3T0-CNqeWnopH1SJD_5NRqVMW3nW3e6AIKZeQhufgpf4zCLXnfQQxuSbantNulSIGRfV_bjb88gf-fuHNODs6S5EgEmxBWVbipLUs4ax9Cw0aJs"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
